# Primary Workflow

Citizen submits report -> AI categorizes + checks for duplicates -> Report attaches to existing Issue OR creates new Issue -> Community verifies issue (weighted confirmations ≥ 3.0 OR LOCAL_BODY_HEAD manual) -> Issue moves into the owning section's queue (category determines section automatically) -> Section head assigns to an officer in their section (HEAD can override directly) -> Employee investigates -> Employee uploads updates -> Employee marks resolved -> Citizen + community verify resolution -> Issue closed OR Issue reopened

If AI detects root cause pattern across 3+ related issues -> Suggestion stored on each Issue -> LOCAL_BODY_HEAD reviews suggestion -> Accepts/edits/rejects -> Root Issue created and issues linked

